{"id":"9992","user":{"id":"337130","nickname":"绝命徒神探","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FpCHOmz10RBEcUMzkZhHX-o75Upr","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【萌新院讲堂】Python教程：Checkbutton组件","content":"<p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><iframe frameborder=\"no\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=191134&amp;auto=1&amp;height=66\"></iframe></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;〖<font color=\"#00ffff\">···前言···</font>〗</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">hi，我是绝命，根据上节课说好的啊，先解释一下代码。（只讲最简单的例子，其他的你们大概就懂了哈）</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">————————————————————————————————————————</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#创建一个主窗口，用于容纳整个GUI程序</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">app=tk.Tk()</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#设置主窗口对象的标题栏</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">app.title(\"萌新院-python\")</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#添加一个Label组件，Label组件是GUI程序中最常用的组件之一</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#Label组件可以显示文本、图标或者图片</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#在这里我们让他显示文本</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">theLabel=tk.Label(app,text=\"窗口程序!\")</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#然后调用Label组件的pack()方法，用于自动调节组件自身的尺寸</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">theLabel.pack()</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#注意，这时候窗口还是不会显示的</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">#除非执行下面这条代码</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">app.mainloop()</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">—————————————————————————————————————————</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">好了就是这样</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;〖<font color=\"#ff0000\">···正文···</font>〗</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">Checkbutton组件就是常见的多选按钮。先来个例子：</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrPdEvTwb8-VT_8Wd7tivXG0OJ5d\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">运行结果：</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FuFB--mOghPBRfYJzrwPaTCo_Q2J\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">恩，勉强可以，就是那个变量v出问题了，先不管他。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;〖<font color=\"#880000\">···尾声···</font>〗</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">恩······</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">这次教程水了，因为没——有——多少——时——间!</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">时间都去哪了？</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">我咋知道？</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">作业：用Checkbutton组件做一个程序，在评论区交给我</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -END-</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1522106690,"created_at":1521892645,"n_views":416,"n_replies":8,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}